official_title: A bill to validate the conveyance of certain land in the State of California by the Southern Pacific Transportation Co..

summary.text: Validates, as far as any interest of the United States is concerned, the conveyance of specified lands in San Bernardino, California, by the Southern Pacific Transportation Company. Reserves to the United States all oil, coal and mineral rights.
